2026-04-19T16:01:22.061+00:00 Now I understand the issue. The `dragPaddingPx: 6` creates a very small grab area around the 72px tiles. On mobile, this is hard to hit. I'll increase the padding to make drag targets more forgiving.
2026-04-19T16:01:22.063+00:00 Done. The hotfix branch `review/shape-sort-mobile-hotfix` is now pushed to origin.

**Change made:** Increased `dragPaddingPx` from 6 → 18 pixels in `public/games/shape-sort/game.js`.

This triples the invisible grab area around each tile (from 84px to 108px effective hit target), making Shape Sort much more usable on phones without changing the visual tile size.
